hey lovies, 
i feel incredibly grateful for all of our wonderful clients, everyone that understands and appreciates our work and mission in this industry. all of you that trust us with their beautiful faces — I am humbled every day by how we can, within a few hours, boost someone’s confidence, make them feel more comfortable in their own skin, by naturally enhancing their features.
I am forever thankful and happy for having a career that I love passionately, for where it has lead me and for all the new learning spaces it is creating for me everyday. 
as a thank you to all of you, I am giving away either a microblading or lip blush session - you decide! :)

For this lovely client of mine it was time for a refresher, after over two years of her last session with me. She has some natural hair in the front and midsection of her brows, however we completely reconstructed the tail of her brows,  since she had no natural hairs in that part of her eyebrow. Loving the result and that I was able to recreate what she was missing, giving her more shape and definition. Tattooed by me at @chi.chi.club

Hi friends, I’m Jette, the visionary behind Chi Chi Club. 
My journey in the beauty industry began in 2008, and since 2015, I’ve passionately delved into the art of microblading. I approach this craft with a holistic and effortlessly natural perspective, striving to redefine the very essence of microblading.

Through my years of experience, I’ve gathered a wealth of knowledge that I’m eager to share. My goal is to positively influence the cosmetic tattooing industry and bring together a community of individuals who appreciate similar aesthetic values. I‘d love to guide you every step of the way, ensuring you feel secure when you start your career journey in microblading. 
Let’s create something beautiful together 🫶🏽

We have just released Chi Chi Academy’s new course for booking online through our website — April 12th to 15th, 2024. Secure your spot now!
